SUMMARY:(Scarborough) Short N' Sweet Morning Hike at Rouge park (5km) *fre
 e hike/parking
DESCRIPTION:GTA Hiking & Stuff\nFree hike and free parking.\n\nMeet at 11a
 m at Glen Rouge Campground.\n\nWe will hike for approx 2 hours at a modera
 te pace (not fast).\n\nOur mid way destination is the hill.\n\nCome prepar
 ed to climb a hill 1 or 2 times (optional challenge).\n\nBring at least 4 
 cups of water and dress appropriately for winter hiking (layers).\n\nBe pr
 epared for water\, mud\, ice and snow on the trail.\n\nMANDATORY: Bring ic
 ers/crampons.\n\nSee you on the trail!\n\nChristine Salib\, M.Ed\, B.Ed (H
 ons.).\nP.T.S.\, N.W.S\, F.I.S\, M.B.S.
